Class Identifier<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.team.workitem.common.model.Identifier<T>

  • public class Identifier<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Identifier of an artifact of a particular type. Overwrites equals(Object) and hashCode() to implement value semantics.
